      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, managed by a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with consistent damping across all EDC modes, and the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle body actuators, addressing key platform concerns. While the aesthetic shows honest wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with exceptional longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
